<template><div><h1 id="os-tmpdir" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#os-tmpdir" aria-hidden="true">#</a> os-tmpdir <a href="https://travis-ci.org/sindresorhus/os-tmpdir" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://travis-ci.org/sindresorhus/os-tmpdir.svg?branch=master" alt="Build Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h1>
<blockquote>
<p>Node.js <a href="https://nodejs.org/api/os.html#os_os_tmpdir" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><code v-pre>os.tmpdir()</code><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://ponyfill.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ponyfill<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
